Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(152,179)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.67,注释,,0,0,0,,翻译  1440kHz
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.78,0:00:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿该数数我的钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to count me money
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.63,0:00:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My money
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你钱不在我这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have your money
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道是谁拿了你的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who took your money
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说  我会让你亲眼看见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me and I'll let you watch
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他被我碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as I tear him into a thousand little pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又被我拼回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mesh 'em back together
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后又被我碎尸万段一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tear him into a thousand little pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all over again
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.50,0:00:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我干的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别把我碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't tear me into a thousand little pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又拼回去  然后再碎尸万段一遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and mesh me back together and tear me to pieces again
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要拿  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要给钱清理打磨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To clean and polish it
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be a sea monkey's uncle
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一批钱来了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's another batch, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包在我身上  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱从来没这么好看过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me money never looked better
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
